      <p begin="5349.511s" xml:id="p997" end="5350.72s">Please!</p>
      <p begin="5351.93s" xml:id="p998" end="5353.515s">Please take me with you too!</p>
      <p begin="5354.224s" xml:id="p999" end="5356.059s">I want to go with you too!</p>
