      <p begin="5373.285s" xml:id="p1003" end="5376.288s">Lower it a bit... carefully...</p>
      <p begin="5392.596s" xml:id="p1004" end="5395.515s">See you, Aki-chan.</p>
      <p begin="5404.19s" xml:id="p1005" end="5405.108s">Ah...</p>
      <p begin="5405.734s" xml:id="p1006" end="5408.862s">Thank you for everything.</p>
      <p begin="5422.292s" xml:id="p1007" end="5426.171s">Akiko. Did you have fun at oba-chan&#039;s house?</p>
      <p begin="5426.254s" xml:id="p1008" end="5427.672s">It was fun.</p>
      <p begin="5427.756s" xml:id="p1009" end="5430.133s">I see. That&#039;s good.</p>
