      <p begin="5599.344s" xml:id="p1029" end="5603.848s">Instead, this plane was fitted with a No. 25 bomb in<br />the nose and a No. 50 bomb in the fuselage.</p>
      <p begin="5605.6s" xml:id="p1030" end="5608.103s">Now, I can finally repay my debt.</p>
      <p begin="5622.617s" xml:id="p1031" end="5623.827s">That&#039;s hilarious...</p>
      <p begin="5628.54s" xml:id="p1032" end="5630.542s">I feel like I want to live.</p>
