      <p begin="6585.037s" xml:id="p1168" end="6586.455s">He chewed them all apart.</p>
      <p begin="6589.666s" xml:id="p1169" end="6592.086s">To Hibiki! We&#039;ll pull from all directions<br />to lift up Godzilla.</p>
      <p begin="6592.169s" xml:id="p1170" end="6593.754s">Full speed ahead at 90 degrees!</p>
      <p begin="6593.837s" xml:id="p1171" end="6596.423s">But the thrust of 2 ships isn&#039;t enough.</p>
      <p begin="6597.007s" xml:id="p1172" end="6598.55s">There&#039;s no other options!</p>
      <p begin="6598.634s" xml:id="p1173" end="6600.01s">Do everything you can!</p>
      <p begin="6600.636s" xml:id="p1174" end="6601.762s">Yes!</p>
      <p begin="6618.362s" xml:id="p1175" end="6621.74s">If this continues, the crane won&#039;t<br />be able to hold it anymore!</p>
      <p begin="6621.824s" xml:id="p1176" end="6623.242s">It&#039;s no good!</p>
      <p begin="6628.08s" xml:id="p1177" end="6628.997s">Ah...</p>
      <p begin="6645.514s" xml:id="p1178" end="6652.354s">This is the Yokohama Tugboat&#039; company&#039;s<br />Fujimaru. We&#039;ll do our best to help out.</p>
      <p begin="6652.896s" xml:id="p1179" end="6653.897s">That voice...</p>
      <p begin="6654.731s" xml:id="p1180" end="6657.526s">It&#039;s Mizushima. Are you the captain?</p>
      <p begin="6658.652s" xml:id="p1181" end="6660.821s">Kid! It&#039;s you?</p>
      <p begin="6661.738s" xml:id="p1182" end="6662.614s">Yes!</p>
      <p begin="6662.698s" xml:id="p1183" end="6666.493s">This is Koeimaru, another ship from Tōyō Kisen.</p>
      <p begin="6666.577s" xml:id="p1184" end="6670.122s">We, the Nikkōmaru from the Yokohama<br />Tugboat Company, will cooperate.</p>
      <p begin="6670.205s" xml:id="p1185" end="6671.999s">Shiokazemaru will assist you.</p>
      <p begin="6672.082s" xml:id="p1186" end="6674.585s">- Tetsuyūmaru.<br />- Nanamimaru.<br />- Minamimaru.</p>
      <p begin="6674.668s" xml:id="p1187" end="6678.046s">きっしょうまる　<br />- Junseimaru.<br />- Heimitsumaru.</p>
      <p begin="6678.13s" xml:id="p1188" end="6680.924s">- Tenyūmaru.<br />- Kaiōmaru.<br />- Yūga.</p>
      <p begin="6681.008s" xml:id="p1189" end="6683.76s">- Chōkamaru.<br />- Jūseimaru.<br />- Taramaru.<br />- Yasagamaru.</p>
      <p begin="6683.844s" xml:id="p1190" end="6686.889s">Please stop calling me &quot;useless!&quot;</p>
      <p begin="6688.765s" xml:id="p1191" end="6690.017s">All right!</p>
      <p begin="6690.1s" xml:id="p1192" end="6691.977s">You don&#039;t say.</p>
      <p begin="6692.06s" xml:id="p1193" end="6695.063s">I&#039;m both surprised and impressed with him.</p>
      <p begin="6695.147s" xml:id="p1194" end="6696.732s">Get the tugboats!</p>
      <p begin="6696.815s" xml:id="p1195" end="6698.775s">All the ships will pull up Godzilla!</p>
      <p begin="6698.859s" xml:id="p1196" end="6700.652s">Get the tugboats</p>
      <p begin="6700.736s" xml:id="p1197" end="6702.696s">Get the tugboats!</p>
      <p begin="6727.304s" xml:id="p1198" end="6730.224s">The depth has started increasing!</p>
      <p begin="6731.642s" xml:id="p1199" end="6734.728s">Come up here, come up here!</p>
      <p begin="6735.229s" xml:id="p1200" end="6737.773s">Depth: 700.</p>
      <p begin="6738.398s" xml:id="p1201" end="6740.4s">Raise, raise, raise...</p>
      <p begin="6771.39s" xml:id="p1202" end="6772.933s">It&#039;s not damaged enough!</p>
      <p begin="6773.892s" xml:id="p1203" end="6776.061s">All ships take evasive action!</p>
      <p begin="6826.903s" xml:id="p1204" end="6828.53s">What&#039;s he going to do?</p>
      <p begin="6828.613s" xml:id="p1205" end="6829.698s">No way!</p>
      <p begin="6833.535s" xml:id="p1206" end="6834.411s">That can&#039;t be!</p>
      <p begin="6834.494s" xml:id="p1207" end="6837.331s">It&#039;s no good! Shikishima!</p>
      <p begin="6864.441s" xml:id="p1208" end="6865.442s">Shikishima...</p>
      <p begin="6880.791s" xml:id="p1209" end="6882.25s">No, that!</p>
      <p begin="6887.13s" xml:id="p1210" end="6888.256s">I see...</p>
      <p begin="6889.966s" xml:id="p1211" end="6891.468s">I see.</p>
      <p begin="6894.137s" xml:id="p1212" end="6897.599s">The crew member escaped safely.</p>
      <p begin="6906.066s" xml:id="p1213" end="6908.652s">This seat serves as an escape device.</p>
      <p begin="6909.82s" xml:id="p1214" end="6911.696s">Pull that lever to activate it.</p>
      <p begin="6915.409s" xml:id="p1215" end="6916.535s">Live.</p>
      <p begin="6919.037s" xml:id="p1216" end="6920.372s">Tachibana-san.</p>
      <p begin="7011.046s" xml:id="p1217" end="7012.13s">Shikishima!</p>
      <p begin="7017.636s" xml:id="p1218" end="7018.762s">You did it!</p>
      <p begin="7019.679s" xml:id="p1219" end="7020.889s">You did it!</p>
      <p begin="7022.974s" xml:id="p1220" end="7024.226s">Kid!</p>
      <p begin="7028.271s" xml:id="p1221" end="7029.105s">Sumiko-san!</p>
      <p begin="7029.189s" xml:id="p1222" end="7030.357s">Kōichi-san!</p>
      <p begin="7031.316s" xml:id="p1223" end="7032.526s">Kōichi-san...</p>
      <p begin="7032.609s" xml:id="p1224" end="7033.818s">Akiko...</p>
      <p begin="7040.325s" xml:id="p1225" end="7041.284s">Eh?</p>
      <p begin="7082.993s" xml:id="p1226" end="7084.744s">Kou-san, is your war...</p>
      <p begin="7086.955s" xml:id="p1227" end="7088.29s">Over?</p>
      <p begin="7101.386s" xml:id="p1228" end="7102.554s">Yep.</p>
      <p begin="7164.407s" xml:id="p1229" end="7169.12s">Subtitles by themirrazz</p>
